Regions Financial to Seek Options for Morgan Keegan After Fraud Settlement

-- B y   V i v e k   S h a n k a r
-- 
2011-06-22T16:41:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-22/regions-financial-to-seek-options-for-morgan-keegan-after-fraud-settlement.html
Regions Financial Corp. (RF)  said it may
sell its Morgan Keegan unit and has hired Goldman, Sachs & Co.
to explore options, after the unit settled fraud allegations
related to subprime mortgage-backed securities.  The Morgan Keegan unit agreed to pay $200 million to settle
the allegations, the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission
said in a separate statement its website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
